OL,5, The family of an eight-year-old boy    
OL,6, whose body was found in woodland more  
OL,7, than 40 years ago has accused police of
OL,8, failing to fully investigate his death.
OL,10,FVishal Mehrotra disappeared from west  
OL,11,FLondon in July 1981, and his remains   
OL,12,Fwere found in Rogate, West Sussex,     
OL,13,Fseven months later.                    
OL,15,FThe BBC has traced a paedophile with   
OL,16,Fpotential links to the case.           
OL,18,FHis family had been told by detectives 
OL,19,Fthe man was believed to have fled to   
OL,20,FAsia but could not be found.           
